  "What is the rule for naming an acid from a polyatomic ion ending in '-ate'?": "",
  "Add the prefix 'hydro-' and suffix '-ic acid'": "",
  "Change '-ate' to '-ic acid' using the element root": "",
  "Change '-ate' to '-ous acid' using the element root": "",
